description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Glutes + Hip Strength with Mini Band' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The The Disciplined Grind vibe means No excuses, no distractions, just execute. This is especially good for When you want pure focus and efficiency..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Engage your hips, glutes, and core with Peter while overlooking the hills of greater Dublin. 

Note: a mini band is recommended....
